overview: Japanese reissue of Janet's #1 2001 album. Includes "Doesn't Really Matter", the #1 title track, "Someone To Call My Lover", "Son Of A Gun", and "Come On Get Up". Special edition inludes a bonus DVD with all of Janet's music videos from the "janet.", "Velvet Rope" and "All For You" albums.
title: Janet Jackson - All For You
